Update (22 Jan): Apologies for the delay, but I have uploaded the 6GB version of the recut. This version also has a few alterations, based on peopleÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s requests, including trimming down the chase sequence through the goblin tunnels; colour correcting the transition from the Misty Mountains to BeornÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s house; taking out the Bombur Ã¢â‚¬Å“barrel bounceÃ¢â‚¬ï¿½ (which is apparently the bane of some peopleÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s existence); and tidying up the final fight on Ravenhill. I have no idea how to remove the gold-coating from Smaug, though. I tried a few variations, but none of them work very well. So, this is the final version of the recut, for good or ill. :P

Now, I do want to temper peopleÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s expectations for the 6GB version. Considering the difference in size, the quality isnÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t dramatically better. Rather, it is somewhere between a DVD and Blu-ray. The screenshots are a good indication. That said, the image is sharper, and the colours are a little more vibrant (than the 2 GB version), so itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s probably preferable for people who would like to watch the recut on a big-screen TV.

